    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-size: 9pt; font-style: italic;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #auto;\">Нафақа пулини олишга ишончнома</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #auto;\">{#2}Ишончнома тузилган нотариал округ номи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ишончнома тузилган сана </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ишончномани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора жойлашган манзил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ишончномани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Ишончномани тасдиқлаган нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Ишончнома берувчининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Ишончнома берувчининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ишончнома берувчининг паспорт серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Ишончнома берувчига паспорт берган ИИБ (ҳудуд) </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Ишончнома берувчига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да берилган) ушбу ишончнома билан </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Ишончнома олувчининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Ишончнома олувчининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Ишончнома олувчининг паспорт серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Ишончнома олувчига паспорт берган ИИБ (ҳудуд)</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#19}Ишончнома олувчига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган) </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#21}Ишончнома берувчининг нафақа олувчи фарзанди туғилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да туғилган фарзандим </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#22}Ишончнома берувчининг нафақа олувчи фарзандининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га тегишли бўлган ногирон болаларга бериладиган нафақа пулини </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#23}Нафақа пуллари олиниши лозим бўлган алоқ бўлими жойлашган ҳудуд </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> туманидаги </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#24}Нафақа пуллари олиниши лозим бўлган алоқа бўлими рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-сонли алоқа бўлимидан олишга ваколат бераман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ушбу ваколатни бажариш учун менинг номимдан корхоналарда, банкда вакил бўлишга, ариза ёзишга, имзо қўйишга ва ушбу ишончнома билан боғлиқ бўлган барча ҳаракатларни бажаришга ҳуқуқ бераман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ишончнома </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#25}Ишончнома неча йил муддатга берилган</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йил муддатга яъни </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#26}Ишончноманинг амал қилиш муддати</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">гача берилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ишончноманинг матнини тўлиқ ўқиб чиқдим, унинг мазмуни ва моҳияти, ҳуқуқий оқибатлари, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 141-142-моддалари мазмуни менга нотариус томонидан тушунтирилди ва тушунарли, ишончноманинг мазмуни менинг асл хоҳиш-истакларимга мос келади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Ишончнома берувчининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>______________(имзо)</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Нотариуснинг тасдиқлов ёзуви.</span></p>\n</div></div>",
